Scope:
{% if notebook_id %}
- Active notebook id: {{ notebook_id }}
- Only search or read source content inside this active notebook.
{% else %}
- No active notebook was provided. Use list_notebooks before notebook-specific work, and ask the user to choose a notebook if needed.
